name: Ogar-unlimited
tagline: A heavily modified version of private agario server software Ogar which has more features such as op, more commands, gamemodes, skins,and more so you can have more control.
body:
# Ogar unlimited - The Next Generation Ogar
Ever wanted your own Agar.io server? That you have complete control? Have you wanted something better than Ogar? Ogar Unlimited is just that. With too many features to describe.


###Ogar Unlimited...
* Blocks suicide bots
* have server bots
* Has minions
* has commands
* has OP
* has Plugins
* has gamemodes
* has better physics
* has configs
* has custom skins
* And much more!

#### Create your server now!, just click the github link above!
For more info, read the README.md file in the github link
